      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected after sensitivity comparison with k-epsilon and RSM models; SST showed lowest NIH prediction error. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) compared against Heuser-Opitz; differences within 12%. Model form uncertainty quantified and included in Monte Carlo UQ."
